body_html:
Maybe it's from your CPU is rather old to support AVX instructions ...
change your tensorflow version to 1.5.0 by "pip install tensorflow==1.5.0"
or search for an unofficial pre-built binary of TF >= 1.6 that does not support AVX
look at this issue in StackOverflow ...
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/50430086/issue-installing-tensorflow-not-a-cuda-cudnn-issue
